# AI Automation Hospital AI Agent -- Environment Variables
# ============================================

# ── Snowflake Connection ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set all three required vars to connect to Snowflake.
# If not set, the app falls back to a local SQLite database.
#
# Sign up for a free 30-day trial (no credit card): https://signup.snowflake.com
# Choose AWS US East or Azure East US for best Cortex AI availability.
#
# SNOWFLAKE_ACCOUNT=your_account.us-east-1
# SNOWFLAKE_USER=your_username
# SNOWFLAKE_PASSWORD=your_password
# SNOWFLAKE_DATABASE=UATAI AUTOMATION HOSPITAL
# SNOWFLAKE_SCHEMA=DBO
# SNOWFLAKE_WAREHOUSE=AI AUTOMATION HOSPITAL_WH
# SNOWFLAKE_ROLE=SYSADMIN

# ── Cortex AI Model ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Which LLM to use for the AI agent explanation.
# Only used when connected to Snowflake.
#
# Cheap (trial-friendly):  llama3.1-8b, snowflake-arctic, mistral-7b
# Better quality:          llama3.1-70b, mistral-large, claude-3-5-sonnet
#
# CORTEX_MODEL=llama3.1-8b

# ── Curtain Packable Statuses ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated Curt_Status.StatusID values considered "packable"
# CURTAIN_PACKABLE_STATUS_IDS=1,2

# ── Redis (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Falls back to in-memory cache if not set
# REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0

# ── Cache TTL ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CACHE_TTL=300
